  "detailed_description": "<strong>Who said it takes time and effort to become a great artist?</strong><br><br>Simply tap to place pieces from up to four different jigsaw puzzles and experiment until you're done! There are no wrong moves, no time limits, and no stress. Leave the pesky rules of art-making behind and focus on the creative process. <br><br>It's your chance to express your creativity without constraint. With no goals or deadlines and no pressure. <br><br>What emerges is a beautiful representation of your own thoughts and feelings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/006f79110fe4ff107ebafd6a71bc451c.webp?t=1683143569\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/3aa0c45ad1909d8b493b4ba12ad3ee95.poster.avif?t=1683143569\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/3aa0c45ad1909d8b493b4ba12ad3ee95.webm?t=1683143569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/3aa0c45ad1909d8b493b4ba12ad3ee95.mp4?t=1683143569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/eb96e8bd3db4bda690a77f96d68d42e9.webp?t=1683143569\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/74bcfec15a7c777cdcdc5612f5cf047e.poster.avif?t=1683143569\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906250/extras/74bcfec15a7c777cdc